content.text:
I have enough to build a clean storage cleanup card. This is a static info card (2x2): total capacity, used space, and a progress ring/bar showing usage ratio, plus a clean-up action.

Let me design it: ring progress showing usage %, with used/total text, and a "立即清理" button.

